---
---
<section id="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="section-title">What It Does</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Complete mediation between AI agents and their tools across every transport.</p>
    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="card pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon icon-magenta">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Govern</h3>
        <p>Centralize policy, ABAC rules, approval workflows, tenant controls, and access decisions. Cedar-compatible policy import/export for AWS AgentCore interoperability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon icon-cyan">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Enforce</h3>
        <p>Inline evaluation on stdio, HTTP, WebSocket, gRPC, and SSE. Fail-closed by default. Injection detection, DLP scanning, and Wasm policy plugins with fuel metering.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon icon-magenta">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Discover</h3>
        <p>Build a live topology graph of MCP servers, tools, and data-flow edges. Fail-closed on unknown tools with Levenshtein suggestions. Drift detection and re-crawl scheduling.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card pillar">
        <div class="pillar-icon icon-cyan">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1" ry="1"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Prove</h3>
        <p>Tamper-evident audit with SHA-256 chains, Merkle proofs, and Ed25519+ML-DSA-65 checkpoints. Export to SIEM (CEF/syslog/OCSF), PostgreSQL, or webhook.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="capabilities-grid">
      <div class="cap">
        <strong>Identity-aware ABAC</strong>
        <span>Agent identity, delegation chains, NHI lifecycle, Cedar-style constraints with forbid overrides.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <strong>Supply chain defense</strong>
        <span>ETDI tool verification, SANDWORM hardening preset, server allowlists, tool-to-server origin binding.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <strong>Injection detection</strong>
        <span>5-layer DLP decode, Aho-Corasick pattern matching, NFKC normalization, ROT13/base64/leetspeak decode.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <strong>Behavioral anomaly</strong>
        <span>Collusion detection, reconnaissance probes, constraint drift, tool capability drift, shadow agent detection.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <strong>Post-quantum ready</strong>
        <span>Hybrid Ed25519+ML-DSA-65 (FIPS 204) signatures on checkpoints and manifests, backward-compatible.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cap">
        <strong>Formally verified</strong>
        <span>132 properties verified across TLA+, Lean 4, Coq, Alloy, and Kani &mdash; fail-closed, determinism, ABAC forbid-override, capability attenuation, and circuit breaker proven, not just tested.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pillars-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
    gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2.5rem}
  .pillar{padding:1.75rem}
  .pillar-icon{width:44px;height:44px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    border-radius:.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;transition:all .2s}
  .icon-magenta{background:rgba(192,75,240,.1);color:var(--magenta)}
  .icon-cyan{background:rgba(50,209,255,.1);color:var(--cyan)}
  .pillar:hover .icon-magenta{background:rgba(192,75,240,.2)}
  .pillar:hover .icon-cyan{background:rgba(50,209,255,.2)}
  .pillar h3{font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;color:var(--text);font-weight:700;transition:color .2s}
  .pillar:hover h3{color:var(--magenta)}
  .pillar p{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}

  .capabilities-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
    gap:1rem;margin-top:2.5rem}
  .cap{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:.5rem;
    padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;border-left:3px solid var(--magenta)}
  .cap strong{display:block;margin-bottom:.25rem;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text)}
  .cap span{font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
</style>
